text:
If anyone needs to borrow my zoom (for unlimited time) today or tomorrow just let me know here or in a DM! I want to make sure you guys have the time and capability to meet and iron out any remaining features/bugs in your code.

Remember that you are each expected to have 3 individually implemented (functional) features for tomorrow's demo for the best outcome.

If you are having trouble fleshing out a feature, I strongly suggest considering an alternative approach or simplification for it. Compromise is okay! You can always build on it later!!

Good luck everyone!
